des:
Chefin Mariam provides you with easy to follow healthy fitness meals with step-by-step instructions. You can ask Mariam for breakfast, dinner, lunch or delicious smoothie recipes. After she provides you with the ingredients, if you change your mind and would like to try another recipe, you can simply ask to change to recipe. 

To get started:
1. Enable skill and Chefin Mariam will ask you to chooce type of recipe, for example: Breakfast, lunch, dinner or smoothie recipe;
2. After you choose the type, Chefin Mariam will suggest you one of the top healthy delicious recipes;
3. After your confirmation, Chefin Mariam will guide you through preparing the mean step by step, is it so much fun cooking with Mariam;
4. Enjoy one of the most delicious meals!
